  <meta property="og:title" content="Scarborough 士嘉堡家庭法律师 | 何淼律师" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="何淼律师为 Scarborough 提供中英双语家庭法服务。647-930-6688。" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://www.miaohelaw.ca/scarborough-family-lawyer" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://www.miaohelaw.ca/scarborough-family-lawyer" />
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"LegalService","name":"何淼律师 — Scarborough 家庭法律师","url":"https://www.miaohelaw.ca/scarborough-family-lawyer","telephone":"+1-647-930-6688","areaServed":{"@type":"City","name":"Scarborough"},"provider":{"@type":"Person","name":"Miao He","alternateName":"何淼"},"inLanguage":["zh","en"]}
  </script>

  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "首页", "item": "https://www.miaohelaw.ca/"},
      {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Scarborough 家庭法律师", "item": "https://www.miaohelaw.ca/scarborough-family-lawyer"}
    ]
  }
  </script>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Scarborough 有说普通话的离婚律师吗？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "有。何淼律师（Miao He）提供普通话及英文双语家庭法服务，服务范围涵盖Scarborough及周边地区，擅长处理华人离婚、子女监护、婚前协议及跨境资产案件。电话：647-930-6688。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Scarborough 离婚需要多长时间？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Ontario 离婚最快约4至6个月（无争议）；如涉及财产分割或子女监护争议，可能需要1至3年。何淼律师会根据您的具体情况制定最有效率的策略。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "何淼律师收费如何？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "初次咨询30分钟收费$220+HST。案件费用视复杂程度而定，何淼律师提供透明收费，咨询后提供书面费用预估。电话：647-930-6688 预约。"
        }
      }
    ]
  }
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">首页</a> › <a href="/contact">服务地区</a> › Scarborough 士嘉堡</div>
        <h1>Scarborough 士嘉堡家庭法律师</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">何淼律师（Miao He）· 中英双语 · 服务士嘉堡全区 · 647-930-6688</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="container content-grid">
        <div class="main-content">
          <div class="definition-box">
            <p>Scarborough 是多伦多东区最大的华人、南亚裔聚居地之一。Agincourt、Scarborough Town Centre 一带华人社区密集，家庭结构多元，法律需求复杂。何淼律师为士嘉堡居民提供专业、贴心的中英双语家庭法服务。</p>
          </div>
          <h2>Scarborough 家庭法服务</h2>
          <p>士嘉堡华人家庭的法律案件常见于：新移民离婚涉及国内婚姻认证、多代同住家庭的财产归属争议，以及子女就读本地还是返回中国的监护权争议。</p>
          <h3>离婚程序与财产分割</h3>
          <p>士嘉堡有大量租住或共同持有房产的家庭。离婚时，婚姻期间的房产增值须进行 Equalization 计算。何淼律师协助厘清婚前房产、父母赠予首付款等复杂情况，确保客户获得公平分配。</p>
          <h3>子女监护与华裔文化背景</h3>
          <p>华裔家庭往往重视子女的中文教育与祖籍文化传承，何淼律师在制定育儿计划时充分考虑这一文化背景，协助将中文学校、农历节日探视等安排纳入正式协议。</p>
          <h3>紧急保护令</h3>
          <p>若面临家庭暴力或子女被带离风险，何淼律师可迅速申请临时限制令（Emergency Restraining Order）或 Ne Exeat 令，防止子女被带出省或出境。</p>
          <div class="qa-block">
            <h3>Q：士嘉堡的家庭法案件在哪个法院处理？</h3>
            <p>A：士嘉堡案件通常在 Scarborough 的 Ontario Court of Justice 或多伦多市中心的 Superior Court of Justice 处理，视案件性质而定。何淼律师可协助判断最适合的法院及程序。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-box">
            <h3>预约 Scarborough 家庭法咨询</h3>
            <p>初次咨询 30 分钟，$220 + HST。中英双语，无需翻译。</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">立即预约</a>
            <a href="tel:6479306688" class="btn-secondary">647-930-6688</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <aside class="sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card"><h3>联系何淼律师</h3><p>📞 <a href="tel:6479306688">647-930-6688</a></p><p>📧 <a href="mailto:miao@miaohelaw.ca">miao@miaohelaw.ca</a></p></div>
          <div class="sidebar-card"><h3>服务项目</h3><ul><li>离婚诉讼</li><li>子女监护</li><li>婚前协议</li><li>财产分割</li><li>抚养费</li><li>跨境资产</li><li>分居协议</li></ul></div>
          <div class="sidebar-card"><h3>服务语言</h3><p>🇨🇳 普通话</p><p>🇨🇦 英文</p></div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</body>
</html>
<style>
  .page-hero{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2C1810 0%,#4A2C1A 100%);color:white;padding:3rem 0 2rem}
  .page-hero h1{font-size:2rem;margin:0.5rem 0;color:#ffffff}.hero-sub{color:#D4A853;margin:0}
  .breadcrumb{font-size:0.85rem;opacity:0.7;margin-bottom:0.5rem}.breadcrumb a{color:white;text-decoration:none}
  .container{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.5rem}.content-section{padding:3rem 0}
  .content-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 300px;gap:3rem}
  .definition-box{background:#FDF6EC;border-left:4px solid #9A8060;padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;margin-bottom:2rem;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0}
  .qa-block{background:#f8f8f8;border-radius:8px;padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;margin:1.5rem 0}
  .qa-block h3{color:#2C1810;margin-top:0;font-size:1rem}
  .cta-box{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2C1810,#4A2C1A);color:white;padding:2rem;border-radius:12px;text-align:center;margin-top:2rem}
  .cta-box h3{margin-top:0;color:#D4A853}
  .btn-primary{display:inline-block;background:#D4A853;color:#2C1810;padding:0.75rem 1.5rem;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;margin:0.5rem}
  .btn-secondary{display:inline-block;background:transparent;color:white;border:2px solid white;padding:0.75rem 1.5rem;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;margin:0.5rem}
  .sidebar{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem}
  .sidebar-card{background:white;border:1px solid #e8e0d5;border-radius:10px;padding:1.2rem}
  .sidebar-card h3{color:#2C1810;font-size:0.95rem;margin-top:0;border-bottom:1px solid #e8e0d5;padding-bottom:0.5rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem}
  .sidebar-card ul{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0}.sidebar-card li{padding:0.3rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0ebe3;font-size:0.9rem}
  .sidebar-card a{color:#9A8060;text-decoration:none}
  h2{color:#2C1810;margin-top:2rem}h3{color:#4A2C1A}
  @media(max-width:768px){.content-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.page-hero h1{font-size:1.5rem}}
</style>
